       http://code.google.com/p/qextserialport/
================================================================================================

= About QextSerialPort =

QextSerialPort provides an interface to old fashioned serial ports for Qt-based applications. It currently supports Mac OS X, Windows, Linux, FreeBSD. 

Please note that:

 * Revision {{{0.9.x}}} is Qt 2 & 3 compatible. 
 * Revision {{{1.x.x}}} is Qt 4 compatible.
 * Revision {{{2.x.x}}} is Qt 5 compatible 

= How to Use =

 * Download the source code 

 * Run following command (or you can use Qt Creator)
     
         qmake
         make
         make install #If you using a system installed Qt5, you will need this

 * Add following line to your application's .pro file

         QT += extserialport

 * Using QextSerialPort in your code, Enjoy it!

         #include "qextserialport.h"
         ....
         QextSerialPort * port = new QextSerialPort();
         ....


